text.section:
The addition under subsection (a) of this section includes the additions required for an individual under:
§ 10-204(b) of this title (Dividends and interest from another state or local obligation);
§ 10-204(c)(2) of this title (Federal tax-exempt income);
§ 10-204(e) of this title (Oil percentage depletion allowance);
§ 10-204(i) of this title (Deduction for qualified production activities income); and
§ 10-204(j) of this title (Deduction for costs for security clearance administrative expenses and construction and equipment costs incurred to construct or renovate a sensitive compartmented information facility).
